name: E-Type II
overview: E-Type II is the sequel to the first E-Type game with slightly improved graphics and gameplay. You still pilots a super duper space fighter as it whizzes around rubble-infested spacelanes but this time it takes ages to destroy space rocks and boulders. You collect money by killing space nasties which are flying around so you can spend it in the shop later. After some time game become dull and not entertaining anymore.
